  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Though <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a> is a smaller skiing destination, they cater well for beginner skiers and young children. Ideally visiting the resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal">Arinsal</a> to start your ski journey is best, with nursery slopes at high-altitude you will have great snow to practise on. The Arinsal Ski School is English speaking and has a superb reputation for beginners.</p>
